<i>noun</i>: 산문 [산ː문] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>산문 [산ː문]</dt><br>
<dd>prose</dd><br>
<dd>글자의 수나 운율 같은 형식을 따르지 않고 소설, 수필 등과 같이 자유롭게 쓴 글.</dd><br>
<dd>A writing such as a novel, an essay, etc., which is created without following a fixed rule like the number of words or metrical format.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>